    <item>
      <title>雷诺承诺通过更便宜的工艺将电动汽车电池成本降低 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/renault-vows-to-lower-ev-battery-costs-20-with-cheaper-process</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷诺公司承诺将电池成本降低 20% 左右，并达成协议在其电动汽车和软件平台上使用更便宜的电池化学成分和新的生产工艺，以保持竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/renault-vows-to-lower-ev-battery-costs-20-with-cheaper-process</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳计划在债务协议达成后于本月启动欧洲债券交易所</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/ghana-aims-to-start-eurobond-exchange-this-month-after-debt-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳财政部长穆罕默德·阿明·亚当表示，在与私人债权人就重组 130 亿美元债务达成原则协议后，加纳预计将于本月启动欧洲债券兑换计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/ghana-aims-to-start-eurobond-exchange-this-month-after-debt-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:43:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国前景黯淡：投资者面临两种不利局面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/france-s-future-narrows-two-unsavoury-scenarios-for-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国提前举行的立法选举首轮结果已将可能的结果缩小至两种——这两种结果都预示着投资者将面临长期的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/france-s-future-narrows-two-unsavoury-scenarios-for-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:34:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 EQT 即将收购价值 30 亿欧元的灰狗车队所有者的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/eqt-is-said-to-near-deal-for-stake-in-3-billion-greyhound-owner</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，EQT AB 即将达成协议，收购 Flix SE 的少数股权，该交易对这家德国公交和火车运营商的估值约为 30 亿欧元（32 亿美元），这进一步推动了近期私募股权交易的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/eqt-is-said-to-near-deal-for-stake-in-3-billion-greyhound-owner</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:17:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
